    "text": "戰士們大家好啊",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 9.1,
    "end": 11.43,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "我是曉臻助教",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 11.63,
    "end": 16.2,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "歡迎來到考前六十天第三十三集",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 16.4,
    "end": 21.98,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "上一集我們算出了地球只有可憐的 0.76% 淡水",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 22.18,
    "end": 26.0,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "對啊那這些珍貴的淡水",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 26.2,
    "end": 28.8,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "到底都藏在哪裡呢",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 29.0,
    "end": 32.32,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "戰士們看這張投影片",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 32.52,
    "end": 35.86,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "最大的寶庫就是地下水",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 36.06,
    "end": 39.79,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "老師地下水是從哪裡來的啊",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 39.99,
    "end": 43.05,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "難道地底下有水龍頭嗎",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 43.25,
    "end": 48.63,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "當然不是啦它的來源其實就是雨水",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 48.83,
    "end": 54.24,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "下雨之後水慢慢滲透進土裡就形成地下水",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 54.44,
    "end": 57.18,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "那地下水在土裡面",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 57.38,
    "end": 60.54,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "會像河流一樣流得很快嗎",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 60.74,
    "end": 63.38,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "這是一個大陷阱喔",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 63.58,
    "end": 68.73,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "地下水在岩石縫隙裡流動速度是非常緩慢的",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 68.93,
    "end": 92.72,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "地下水流速極慢，且水面隨地形與季節起伏",
    "is_pinned": true,
    "pin_level": 1,
    "commands": [
      "釘選",
      "地下水流速極慢，且水面隨地形與季節起伏"
    ]
  },
  {
    "start": 74.49,
    "end": 76.99,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "而且投影片上說",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 77.19,
    "end": 80.32,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "地下水面不一定是平的耶",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 80.52,
    "end": 84.49,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "沒錯它會跟著地形起伏",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 84.69,
    "end": 89.52,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "而且旱季跟雨季的地下水面高度也會不一樣喔",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 92.72,
    "end": 96.33,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "老師旁邊那個圖有分層耶",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 96.53,
    "end": 99.99,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "什麼是透水層跟不透水層啊",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 100.19,
    "end": 103.63,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "這就像是海綿跟保鮮膜",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 103.83,
    "end": 108.5,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "透水層就像海綿縫隙很大可以吸水",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 108.7,
    "end": 112.16,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "最常見的岩石就是砂岩",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 112.36,
    "end": 115.51,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "那不透水層就是保鮮膜囉",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 115.71,
    "end": 118.34,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "水完全穿不過去",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 118.54,
    "end": 123.73,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "答對了像是頁岩就是不透水層",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 123.93,
    "end": 128.33,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "水滲不下去就會積在透水層裡面",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 128.53,
    "end": 183.56,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "透水層是砂岩像海綿，不透水層是頁岩像保鮮膜",
    "is_pinned": true,
    "pin_level": 1,
    "commands": [
      "釘選",
      "透水層是砂岩像海綿，不透水層是頁岩像保鮮膜"
    ]
  },
  {
    "start": 133.92,
    "end": 136.4,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "充滿水的這一層",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 136.6,
    "end": 139.8,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "就叫做圖上的飽和帶對吧",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 140.0,
    "end": 145.1,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "沒錯接著我們來看下面的水井",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 145.3,
    "end": 149.17,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "只要往下挖挖到地下水面以下",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 149.37,
    "end": 152.28,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "就可以開始抽水了對吧",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 152.48,
    "end": 156.06,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "是的這是普通的水井",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 156.26,
    "end": 159.78,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "但還有一種不用馬達的自流井喔",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 159.98,
    "end": 164.42,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "自流井難道水會自己噴出來嗎",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 164.62,
    "end": 169.58,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "沒錯這是利用連通管原理",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 169.78,
    "end": 174.9,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "如果井口比地下水面還要低水就會受壓力自動噴出",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 175.1,
    "end": 183.56,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "自流井：利用連通管原理，井口需低於地下水面",
    "is_pinned": true,
    "pin_level": 2,
    "commands": [
      "釘選",
      "自流井：利用連通管原理，井口需低於地下水面"
    ]
  },
  {
    "start": 183.56,
    "end": 186.02,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "哇太神奇了",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 186.22,
    "end": 190.18,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "那我們不就可以無限瘋狂抽地下水了嗎",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 190.38,
    "end": 195.91,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "千萬不行戰士們請看最後一個重點",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 196.11,
    "end": 199.12,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "超抽地下水的影響",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 199.32,
    "end": 203.02,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "哎呀投影片寫會地層下陷耶",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 203.22,
    "end": 207.91,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "對想像充滿水的海綿水被抽光了",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 208.11,
    "end": 211.29,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "海綿就會整個被壓扁",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 211.49,
    "end": 215.41,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "一旦地層下陷就再也回不去了喔",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 215.61,
    "end": 218.93,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "而且如果是靠近海邊的地方",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 219.13,
    "end": 222.14,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "還會發生很可怕的事喔",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 222.34,
    "end": 227.89,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "沒錯沒有了地下水的壓力海水就會灌進來",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 228.09,
    "end": 232.01,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "造成地下水鹹化跟海水倒灌",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 232.21,
    "end": 235.24,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "這塊土地就徹底毀了",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 235.44,
    "end": 238.59,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "戰士們一定要把地層下陷",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 238.79,
    "end": 242.04,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "跟地下水鹹化畫上大星星",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 242.24,
    "end": 251.21,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "超抽地下水：導致地層下陷不可逆與地下水鹹化",
    "is_pinned": true,
    "pin_level": 1,
    "commands": [
      "釘選",
      "超抽地下水：導致地層下陷不可逆與地下水鹹化"
    ]
  },
  {
    "start": 251.21,
    "end": 254.62,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "戰士們請閉上眼睛",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 254.82,
    "end": 257.23,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "好好想一下喔",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 257.43,
    "end": 261.64,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "如果我們想在地底蓋一座天然地下水庫",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 261.84,
    "end": 265.95,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "水庫的底部應該要是砂岩還是頁岩呢",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 266.15,
    "end": 269.88,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "當然是要用不透水的保鮮膜頁岩啊",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 270.08,
    "end": 273.09,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "不然水全部都漏光光了",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 273.29,
    "end": 278.05,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "漂亮這就是滿級分戰士",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 278.25,
    "end": 281.28,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "該有的解題反射神經",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 281.48,
    "end": 284.08,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "我是彥君老師",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 284.28,
    "end": 286.62,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "我是曉臻助教",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 286.82,
    "end": 290.35,
    "speaker": "合聲",
    "text": "珍貴淡水永續相隨",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
